        <div class="blog-hero-content">
          <h1>Best Date Night Restaurants in Venice</h1>
          <p class="blog-subtitle">Discover 13 romantic dining spots in LA's most eclectic beach neighborhood</p>
          <div class="blog-meta">
            <span class="publish-date">Published: October 15, 2025</span>
            <span class="read-time">Reading time: 8 minutes</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>

      <!-- Introduction -->
      <section class="blog-intro">
        <p>Venice is one of Los Angeles' most unique neighborhoods, combining bohemian beach culture with a vibrant culinary scene. With 13 exceptional date night restaurants, this eclectic community offers everything from casual beachside cafes to upscale dining experiences perfect for romantic evenings.</p>
        
        <p>Whether you're looking for a sunset dinner by the ocean, an intimate wine bar, or a trendy spot along Abbot Kinney Boulevard, Venice's diverse dining landscape has something for every couple. From the famous Venice Beach Boardwalk to the chic boutiques and restaurants of Abbot Kinney, discover the perfect spot for your next romantic dinner.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- Quick Stats -->
      <section class="blog-stats">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">{veniceRestaurants.length}</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Restaurants</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">{avgDateScore}</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Avg Date Score</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">{upscaleCount}</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Upscale Options</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">{cuisineTypes.length}</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Cuisine Types</div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Top Restaurants -->
