                <span class="price">{'$'.repeat(restaurant.price_level)}</span>
                <span class="date-score">Date Score: {restaurant.date_night_score}</span>
              </div>
              <p class="restaurant-description">{restaurant.description || `A romantic dining experience in Venice perfect for date nights.`}</p>
              <a href={`/losangeles/${restaurant.slug}/`} class="btn btn-primary">View Details</a>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Neighborhood Highlights -->
      <section class="neighborhood-highlights">
        <h2>Why Venice is Perfect for Date Nights</h2>
        
        <div class="highlights-grid">
          <div class="highlight-card">
            <h3>üèñÔ∏è Beachside Ambiance</h3>
            <p>Venice offers unique beachfront and canalside dining experiences, creating a relaxed and romantic atmosphere perfect for couples who love the ocean.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="highlight-card">
            <h3>üé® Bohemian Culture</h3>
            <p>The neighborhood's artistic and creative vibe adds character to every dining experience, making each date night feel special and unique.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="highlight-card">
            <h3>üåÖ Sunset Views</h3>
            <p>Many restaurants offer stunning sunset views over the Pacific Ocean, creating unforgettable romantic moments for couples.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="highlight-card">
            <h3>üö∂ Walkable Streets</h3>
            <p>The pedestrian-friendly Abbot Kinney Boulevard and Venice Beach Boardwalk make it easy to stroll between restaurants, cafes, and entertainment for a complete evening out.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Cuisine Diversity -->
      <section class="cuisine-diversity">
        <h2>Diverse Culinary Experiences</h2>
        <p>Venice's restaurant scene reflects LA's eclectic dining landscape, offering couples the opportunity to explore cuisines from around the world:</p>
        
        <ul class="cuisine-list">
          {cuisineTypes.slice(0, 8).map(cuisine => (
            <li><a href={`/cuisines/${cuisine.toLowerCase().replace(/\s+/g, '-')}/`}>{cuisine.replace(/_/g, ' ')}</a></li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        
        <p>From authentic Italian trattorias to modern farm-to-table concepts, each restaurant brings its own unique atmosphere and culinary expertise to create memorable date night experiences.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- Planning Your Date Night -->
      <section class="planning-tips">
        <h2>Planning Your Venice Date Night</h2>
        
        <div class="tips-grid">
          <div class="tip-card">
            <h3>üïê Best Times to Visit</h3>
            <p>Weekday evenings offer a more relaxed atmosphere with easier parking. Weekend nights are livelier but can be crowded‚Äîreservations are highly recommended.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="tip-card">
            <h3>üÖøÔ∏è Parking Tips</h3>
            <p>Street parking can be challenging in Venice, especially near the beach. Consider parking a few blocks away or using ride-sharing services for convenience.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="tip-card">
            <h3>üëó Dress Code</h3>
            <p>Venice embraces a casual, laid-back vibe, but some restaurants are more upscale. Check restaurant websites for specific dress codes, but smart casual works for most spots.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="tip-card">
            <h3>üåä Beach Walk</h3>
            <p>Many couples enjoy a romantic walk on Venice Beach before or after dinner. The boardwalk offers street performers, shops, and stunning ocean views.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Related Content -->
      <section class="related-content">
        <h2>Explore More Date Night Options</h2>
        <div class="related-links">
          <a href="/losangeles/restaurants/neighborhoods/venice/" class="related-link">
            <h3>All Venice Restaurants</h3>
            <p>Browse our complete list of {veniceRestaurants.length} restaurants in Venice</p>
          </a>
          
          <a href="/losangeles/restaurants/neighborhoods/santa-monica/" class="related-link">
            <h3>Santa Monica Restaurants</h3>
            <p>Discover romantic oceanfront dining in neighboring Santa Monica</p>
          </a>
          
          <a href="/losangeles/restaurants/neighborhoods/manhattan-beach/" class="related-link">
            <h3>Manhattan Beach Restaurants</h3>
            <p>Explore more beachside dining options south of Venice</p>
          </a>
          
          <a href="/blog/outdoor-dining-los-angeles/" class="related-link">
            <h3>Outdoor Dining in LA</h3>
            <p>Find the perfect outdoor dining spots for romantic evenings</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Call to Action -->
      <section class="cta-section">
        <h2>Ready for Your Next Date Night?</h2>
        <p>With 13 exceptional restaurants to choose from, Venice offers endless possibilities for romantic dining. Whether you're planning a special celebration or a casual beachside date, you're sure to find the perfect spot.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/losangeles/restaurants/neighborhoods/venice/" class="btn btn-primary">View All Venice Restaurants</a>
          <a href="/losangeles/restaurants/" class="btn btn-secondary">Explore All LA Restaurants</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

